STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Timothy Eric SMELTSER, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0998 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Following a guilty plea, Timothy Smeltser appeals his sentence. SENTENCE AFFIRMED IN PART, VACATED IN PART, AND REMANDED.

SENTENCE AFFIRMED IN PART, VACATED IN PART, AND REMANDED.
